\u001B[1mDESCRIPTION\u001B[0m
    This bundle provides the Karaf shell commands to manipulate DS Components.

    The following commands are available:
    \u001B[36mscr:activate\u001B[0m Adds a list of repository URLs to the features service.
    \u001B[36mscr:deactivate\u001B[0m Shows information about selected information.
    \u001B[36mscr:details\u001B[0m Installs a feature with the specified name and version.
    \u001B[36mscr:list\u001B[0m Lists all existing features available from the defined repositories.

